{"tid":2183536,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙名將 大衛施華 確診","createTime":"2020-09-01T04:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T04:00:13.000Z","uid":189046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0983a8d47a394f8bf569fb010569df0aff9c2ac6","tid":2183536,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【Now Sports】剛回流西甲的西班牙中場名將大衛施華，確診新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n據多個英國及西班牙傳媒透露，於去季結束後離開曼城的中場名將大衛施華（David Silva），改投皇家蘇斯達後接受新型冠狀病毒檢測，結果證實這位34歲中場呈陽性反應，並沒任何徵狀的他現正自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n施華日前才出席加盟皇蘇的記者會，他指自己依然是個很有競爭力的球員。施華的皇家蘇斯達隊友奧耶沙巴，較早前同樣因為確診，已退出西班牙國家隊大軍，無緣在歐洲國家聯賽上陣。<br />\n<br />\n曾代表國家隊上陣7次的奧耶沙巴，在社交網絡說：「我想公告大家我在最近一次測試中呈陽性反應。我必需留在家中數天，不能為國家隊效力。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/2/082/30599644082/30607865259_600x337.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F2%2F082%2F30599644082%2F30607865259_600x337.jpg&h=b105d609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=30599644082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D30599644082&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7q%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=e6025d7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=30599644082</a>"}]}